---
title: Sesame-Crusted Salmon & Garlic Spring Onion Rice with Ginger-Soy Veggies & Pickled Onion
description: Go fishing for compliments with this sublime salmon dish – anyone who tastes the crispy skin speckled with sesame seeds,
the moreish spring onion and garlic rice or the sharp pickled onion is going to be falling at your feet in appreciation!

